---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="SMS Program — Plenum AI Systems"
  description="Learn about the Plenum AI Systems SMS program, including how to opt in, opt out, and get help. A2P 10DLC compliant."
  canonical="https://plenumaisystems.com/sms">

<Nav />

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="label">SMS Program</div>
    <h1>Text Messaging Program</h1>
    <p>Everything you need to know about our SMS program — how to opt in, opt out, and get help.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="legal-content">

      <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: June 28, 2026</p>

      <h2>Program Description</h2>
      <p><strong>Lead Continuity LLC</strong>, doing business as (DBA) <strong>Plenum AI Systems</strong>, operates an SMS (text messaging) program to keep you informed about our services, campaigns, and updates. Our program is fully compliant with A2P 10DLC regulations and the Telephone Consumer Protection Act (TCPA).</p>
      <p>By opting in, you may receive text messages in the following categories:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Marketing Messages:</strong> Special offers, promotional content, service updates, and marketing materials.</li>
        <li><strong>Non-Marketing Messages:</strong> Appointment reminders, lead follow-up, and service notifications.</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="sms-info-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:24px;margin-top:32px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>📱 How to Opt In</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Visit our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a> and fill out the form.</li>
            <li>Check the consent box(es) for the type of messages you wish to receive.</li>
            <li>Provide your phone number.</li>
            <li>Submit the form — your opt-in is recorded with a timestamp.</li>
          </ul>
          <p style="margin-top:16px;font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--text3);">Consent is voluntary. Opting in is not a condition of purchasing any goods or services.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>🚫 How to Opt Out</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Reply <strong>STOP</strong> to any text message from us.</li>
            <li>You will receive a final confirmation message.</li>
            <li>No further messages will be sent after confirmation.</li>
            <li>You may re-opt-in at any time by providing consent again.</li>
          </ul>
          <p style="margin-top:16px;font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--text3);">You can also contact us directly to opt out.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>❓ Need Help?</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Reply <strong>HELP</strong> to any text message from us.</li>
            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:contact@plenumaisystems.com">contact@plenumaisystems.com</a></li>
            <li>Phone: <a href="tel:+130****4737">+1 (307) 296-4737</a></li>
            <li>Address: 30 N Gould St Ste N, Sheridan, WY 82801</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>📊 Message Details</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Message frequency:</strong> Varies, up to 4 messages per month.</li>
            <li><strong>Message &amp; data rates:</strong> May apply. Check with your carrier.</li>
            <li><strong>Supported carriers:</strong> AT&amp;T, Verizon, T-Mobile, Sprint, and most regional carriers.</li>
            <li><strong>Age restriction:</strong> You must be 18+ to participate.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>Carriers</h2>
      <p>Our SMS program is supported by most major mobile carriers, including but not limited to AT&amp;T, Verizon, T-Mobile, and Sprint. Lead Continuity LLC DBA Plenum AI Systems is not responsible for any delays or failures in message delivery by your mobile carrier. Message delivery is subject to effective transmission from your mobile carrier's network.</p>

      <h2>Privacy &amp; Data</h2>
      <p>Your phone number and opt-in data are protected under our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>. No mobile information will be shared with third parties/affiliates for marketing/promotional purposes. Information sharing to subcontractors in support services, such as customer service, is permitted.</p>

      <h2>Terms</h2>
      <p>By participating in our SMS program, you agree to our <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>. Please review them for complete details on program terms, cancellation, and your rights.</p>

      <div style="margin-top:48px;padding:24px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);">
        <p><strong>Contact Us:</strong> If you have any questions about our SMS program, please reach out to us at <a href="mailto:contact@plenumaisystems.com">contact@plenumaisystems.com</a> or call <a href="tel:+130****4737">+1 (307) 296-4737</a>.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<Footer />

</BaseLayout>
